Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为何不响应归顺的号召
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.17,0:00:14.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会归顺维拉尔大人的仇人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.14,0:00:27.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,愿阿尔图克荣光常在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.48,0:00:32.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这座城和王座就交给你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.28,0:00:37.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这不意味着阿尔图克败北了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.37,0:00:40.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.33,0:00:42.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是我在统治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.41,0:00:44.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那这里就不是阿尔图克了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.25,0:00:46.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而是达尔塔尼亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.58,0:00:50.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的  你这维拉尔大人的仇人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.92,0:00:55.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.05,0:00:58.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.30,0:01:01.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,活着毫无作为的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.52,0:01:08.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,死了又能有何作为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.39,0:02:57.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,令人悔恨的是在先前的战斗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.60,0:02:59.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔图克伯爵丧命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.14,0:03:04.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们不能一直沉浸在悲伤之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.73,0:03:09.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔林德  达尔塔尼亚  诺尔德的进攻想必还会持续下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.53,0:03:10.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了与他们对抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.28,0:03:13.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须团结起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.49,0:03:20.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在今天聚集了众多继承阿尔图克伯爵维拉尔•康斯坦斯意志的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.62,0:03:23.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,经大家认可的基础上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.63,0:03:27.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我宣布阿尔图克条约成立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.81,0:03:41.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢谁来当盟主啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.73,0:03:52.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔大人的亲弟弟赛尔杰阁下才是最合适的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.07,0:03:56.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,诚然我也想为兄长报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.62,0:03:59.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但我没这个能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.54,0:04:00.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.87,0:04:03.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,赛尔杰大人的想法是正因为想夺回祖国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.41,0:04:08.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才该任命拉席克・达维多为盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.84,0:04:14.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此拉席克阁下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.30,0:04:16.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得很合适
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.43,0:04:18.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.68,0:04:22.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉我无法当盟主啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.89,0:04:24.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为我的爵位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.31,0:04:28.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是提欧•科尔内罗大人暂时交给我保管的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.52,0:04:34.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得拉席克阁下原本是提欧阁下的从属君主吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.65,0:04:38.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的我准备有朝一日再次为他效劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.66,0:04:42.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我个人认为提欧大人才是条约盟主合适人选
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.00,0:04:44.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,各位意下如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我可反对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.04,0:04:52.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧阁下曾经击退过瓦尔林德军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.46,0:04:55.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在对方看来就是仇敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他当上了盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.39,0:04:59.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必敌人会全力攻过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.76,0:05:03.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无论谁当盟主同盟都不会手下留情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.89,0:05:06.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且联合什么都办不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.48,0:05:12.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们的盟主必须是大家都认可的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.48,0:05:16.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而那个人不是提欧阁下是拉席克阁下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.11,0:05:20.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,很荣幸有那么多人期待我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.03,0:05:24.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这是我跟提欧大人的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.25,0:05:26.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉席克的忠心让我很感激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.42,0:05:31.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在场的君主希望由你来担任盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.05,0:05:37.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说大家认为我没资格让你从属于我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.59,0:05:38.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.30,0:05:42.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,选谁当盟主是你们决定的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.51,0:05:44.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我也有尊严
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.56,0:05:48.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我想证明自己是否有资格让拉席克效力于我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.94,0:05:50.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如何证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.86,0:05:52.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在今后的战斗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.40,0:05:55.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我会立下让所有人心服口服的战功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.65,0:05:59.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知你打算活跃成什么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.07,0:06:02.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是主从之间的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.16,0:06:07.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得让拉席克阁下和提欧阁下决定就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.08,0:06:11.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们只需当二位的证人就可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.42,0:06:15.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么现在就任命拉席克阁下为盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.30,0:06:17.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,等有结果了再重新决定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.97,0:06:19.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.51,0:06:20.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我赞成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.72,0:06:22.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.31,0:06:27.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让我进攻莱加里亚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.43,0:06:32.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽娜大人说开始进攻后就全由您判断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.31,0:06:35.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,征服莱加里亚也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.32,0:06:37.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不战斗直接撤退也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.61,0:06:38.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.07,0:06:42.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽娜阁下准备夺回布鲁塔巴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.78,0:06:45.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是让我们威胁敌人后方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.41,0:06:48.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,应该如您所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.29,0:06:50.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我会留五百人左右守城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的全部出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.46,0:06:53.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,以莱加里亚为开端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.04,0:06:56.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不断征服先前奉维拉尔为盟主的地区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.26,0:07:00.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候阿尔图克的君主们也不得不归顺了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.76,0:07:02.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.01,0:07:04.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得不行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.10,0:07:08.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据说以莱加里亚为首的诸国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.47,0:07:11.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,将拉席克风为盟主并缔结了条约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,准备奋起反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.90,0:07:15.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,无论敌人是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,都不是达尔塔尼亚的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.73,0:07:19.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉席克应该是个值得提防的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.86,0:07:22.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就算是他也无法出现在每一个战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.20,0:07:23.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.53,0:07:25.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是在下认为在此次战斗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.87,0:07:29.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,认清敌人的实力很关键
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为何要对我提意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.12,0:07:34.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你是马丽娜阁下的契约魔法师吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.71,0:07:37.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在被派遣到米尔扎阁下身边了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.26,0:07:42.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么从下次开始就堂堂正正的进言吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.34,0:07:49.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 你得做好心理准备别触怒我被杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.18,0:07:50.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.62,0:08:12.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只能说米尔扎太子的统率力很强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.54,0:08:16.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让士兵们去预定的地方待机吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.08,0:08:20.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来请赛尔杰大人当一回诱饵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.17,0:08:20.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.77,0:08:35.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,别管撤退的军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,全军一起追击赛尔杰•康斯坦斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.12,0:08:50.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉席克•达维多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.58,0:08:52.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.42,0:09:00.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是我能对付的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.46,0:09:03.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里士兵的损伤轻微
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.17,0:09:05.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,面对米尔扎这样的调兵很精彩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.84,0:09:07.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.47,0:09:14.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好了来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.77,0:09:56.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉席克大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.40,0:10:03.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我的脑袋还连着的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.36,0:10:05.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,米尔扎・库切斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.49,0:10:08.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怕的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉席克•达维多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.99,0:10:15.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是等闲之辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.50,0:10:21.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,伊戈尔・康斯坦斯的军队啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.67,0:10:24.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在攻过去对我方不利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.55,0:10:26.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.17,0:10:28.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,返回本国了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.81,0:10:38.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,错失杀死拉席克的机会了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.44,0:10:44.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,城主是提欧・科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.44,0:10:46.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵数量约为三千
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.28,0:10:49.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,三干比想象中多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.78,0:10:52.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到在这么少的时间里招来这么多士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.24,0:10:58.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得那时候应该让他归顺吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.16,0:11:01.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是马丽娜大人决定的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.50,0:11:05.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊我并非后悔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.67,0:11:14.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我不想跟他及其契约魔法师西露卡•梅蕾蒂斯战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧•科尔内罗在阿尔图克条约中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.85,0:11:19.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,宣布要跟同盟开战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.81,0:11:23.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毋容置疑他是必须讨伐的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这我自然知道；
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在开战前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.27,0:11:28.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我想先跟他见一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.78,0:11:34.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,需要安排一场会谈吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.33,0:11:39.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,会谈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.33,0:11:41.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种状况下谈什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谈判毫无意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.83,0:11:46.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔林德打算夺回这片土地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.34,0:11:49.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们也不能撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.51,0:11:49.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.92,0:11:55.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是父亲应该也明白这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.64,0:11:58.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是马丽娜大人想见提欧大人一面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.10,0:11:59.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,见我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.43,0:12:03.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔林德的大军实力超过了我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.48,0:12:07.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲这时候也不会使用什么计谋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.48,0:12:11.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕马丽娜大人只是单纯对提欧大人感兴趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.15,0:12:15.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此既然是这样就见一面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.91,0:12:17.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想跟她说点话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.78,0:12:22.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,估计你父亲也会一同出席会谈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.66,0:12:26.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的我还以为再也见不到父亲了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,果然想见一面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.05,0:12:31.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.80,0:12:35.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你很怕父亲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.97,0:12:40.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,身为魔法师的父亲的确是个冷酷无情的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.93,0:12:45.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在上魔法大学的时候他差点杀了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.52,0:12:47.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为违反规定我差点被剔除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是没办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.69,0:12:57.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲只是遵守了魔法师协会的规定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.53,0:12:59.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不至于取你性命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.78,0:13:04.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此他依然是我父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.75,0:13:08.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.55,0:13:16.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系现在还没开始会谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.87,0:13:42.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.70,0:13:46.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好年轻啊  跟传闻一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,边境伯爵跟传闻不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.13,0:13:52.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很温柔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.09,0:13:56.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,身边也有人这么说我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.88,0:13:59.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯大人也是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.80,0:14:00.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.05,0:14:04.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人将我称作朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.06,0:14:05.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.43,0:14:11.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿莱克希斯大人依然真心思念着马丽娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.40,0:14:14.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我还是希望二位能走在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.15,0:14:18.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是哈鲁西亚公爵的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.41,0:14:21.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧阁下也是梦想家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.32,0:14:24.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过阿尔图克伯爵也跟我这么说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.04,0:14:26.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔大人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.33,0:14:30.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那是他最后的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.33,0:14:32.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.50,0:14:33.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.67,0:14:36.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好 阿莱克希斯也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.34,0:14:42.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没发现有人不希望混沌时代结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.22,0:14:48.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我决心用武力统一大陆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.69,0:14:50.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要大战持续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.31,0:14:53.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,圣印早晚会统一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.02,0:14:58.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来暗中蠢动的人也会现身了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.53,0:15:02.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,您打算击败那些人创建由君主统治的时代吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.99,0:15:04.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是君主嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.45,0:15:08.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这种做法会造成众多流血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.58,0:15:09.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我已有觉悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.04,0:15:19.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我想重拾马丽娜大人放弃的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.80,0:15:21.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下能办到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.26,0:15:22.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能办到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.01,0:15:26.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在场的西露卡为我指明了道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.85,0:15:27.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.10,0:15:33.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,话说提欧阁下为了西露卡阁下舍弃了爵位啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.73,0:15:36.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是思考并选择了重要的事物而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.19,0:15:38.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.28,0:15:43.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过对我而言更重要的不是阿莱克希斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.45,0:15:47.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是瓦尔林德是大工房同盟仅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.83,0:15:49.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.29,0:15:52.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不想跟提欧阁下开战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.83,0:15:54.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但我必须夺回此地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.17,0:15:57.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也不想跟马丽娜大人开战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.17,0:15:59.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但我绝不能撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.84,0:16:03.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.34,0:16:07.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,下次就在战场相见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.27,0:16:16.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无疑问玛丽娜大人仍爱着阿莱克希斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.48,0:16:19.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我想尽为让他们走在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.11,0:16:22.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要实现这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.61,0:16:24.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕需要奇迹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.95,0:16:27.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此能不能为我创造奇迹呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.28,0:16:30.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这可难倒我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.71,0:16:35.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定要让同盟和联合议和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.58,0:16:38.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让马丽娜大人和阿莱克希斯大人走在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.71,0:16:41.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,把大圣堂的惨剧转变为奇迹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.81,0:17:00.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人  现在可不是干这种事的时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.07,0:17:02.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就是干这种事的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.66,0:17:09.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了二位的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.16,0:17:13.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了二位的爱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.25,0:17:25.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说您是为了挑畔马丽娜大人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.13,0:17:28.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想让她想起来什么才是堇要的而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.39,0:17:33.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要赢得这场战斗很难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.85,0:17:37.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们的目标是大陆的人从未想过的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.73,0:17:40.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能死在这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.40,0:17:44.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我羞得现在就要死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.95,0:17:53.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭爱是保不住城的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.33,0:17:55.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,国家和人民也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽娜大人有报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.59,0:18:04.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔林德军撤退了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.88,0:18:06.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据说在北方的战斗中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.22,0:18:11.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,卢克莱尔伯爵克鲁特•凯拉斯击败了诺尔德•埃里克率领的同盟军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.10,0:18:13.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,目前还在追击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.85,0:18:17.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这会导致瓦尔林德后方遭受威胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.14,0:18:19.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必撤退的原因在此吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.15,0:18:22.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人这是好机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.73,0:18:25.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,由于瓦尔林德已撤军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.44,0:18:28.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在接下来的一段时间里  大陆的主战场恐怕会转移至北方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.49,0:18:31.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正是前往西斯迪纳的好机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.41,0:18:37.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人说过要将大圣堂的惨剧转变为奇迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.41,0:18:40.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还说想让二人结婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.13,0:18:43.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了实现这个理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.38,0:18:48.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,必须获得与阿莱克希斯大人和马丽娜大人对等的地位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.84,0:18:54.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说提欧大人必须成为阿尔图克条约的盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.47,0:18:56.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为此就得打倒罗西尼家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.64,0:18:59.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,将西斯迪纳从暴政中解放出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.77,0:19:02.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正是实现提欧大人最初的誓言的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.23,0:19:08.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就用这个战功获得条约的君主们认可吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.16,0:19:13.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我会为您指路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.00,0:19:19.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.79,0:19:24.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,罗西尼手下有众多忠诚从属君主和士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.59,0:19:27.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想进攻至少要一万兵力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.59,0:19:29.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还在跟同盟打仗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.84,0:19:31.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,兵哪够分啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.93,0:19:35.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果大军出击就无法证明提欧大人的力量了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.05,0:19:38.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们不会借助其他君主的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.85,0:19:41.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就只靠我们前往西斯迪纳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.85,0:19:42.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,做梦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.27,0:19:44.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.23,0:19:52.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一来  条约的君主们篦不得不认可战功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.78,0:19:56.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后这样一来  他们也不会反对我让岀盟主的位置了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.03,0:19:59.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,莫雷诺立刻通知君主们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.29,0:20:02.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了履行会议时的宣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.54,0:20:05.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人要前去解放西斯迪纳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.54,0:20:06.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.17,0:20:10.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这边就交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.13,0:20:13.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你就去故乡兑现自己的誓言吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.09,0:20:14.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.96,0:22:07.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.54,0:22:10.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.46,0:22:12.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧•科尔内罗要来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.50,0:22:14.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你说科尔内罗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.17,0:22:15.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那人的子孙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.63,0:22:17.63,zhengzhong,,0,0,0,,只是他自称的而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.43,0:22:22.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  就是父亲之前在君主会议上见过的君主啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.31,0:22:26.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他貌似说过早晚会回这座岛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.35,0:22:34.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知他打算在这由罗西尼家统治的岛上干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.61,0:22:36.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过要说科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.49,0:22:38.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在这座岛上就是英雄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.65,0:22:41.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,用这名号的人要来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.82,0:22:43.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是来者不善吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.41,0:22:45.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,朱泽尔说的没错
